msgstr "Táto voľba má vplyv len keď je zobrazený súhrnný blok."

#: resources/views/settings.phtml:197
msgid "Summary statistics cannot be shown while the summary block is disabled."
msgstr ""
"Súhrnná štatistika sa nemôže zobraziť, pokiaľ nie je zobrazený súhrnný blok."

#: resources/views/settings.phtml:203
msgid "Show summary statistics"
msgstr "Zobraziť štatistický súhrn"

#: resources/views/settings.phtml:211
msgid "How should empty parts of extended family be presented?"
msgstr "Ako zobraziť prázdne bloky?"

#: resources/views/settings.phtml:213
msgid ""
"The option to collect messages about empty family parts at the summary block "
"only has an effect if the summary block is shown."
msgstr ""
"Voľba zobrazenia prázdnych blokov v sumárnom bloku je možná, len pokiaľ je "
"zvolené zobrazenie sumárneho bloku."

#: resources/views/settings.phtml:216
msgid ""
"Empty family parts cannot be collected at the summary block while the "
"summary block is disabled."
msgstr ""
"Prázdne bloky sa môžu zbierať do súhrnu len pokiaľ je zvolené zobrazenie "
"sumárneho bloku."

#: resources/views/settings.phtml:222
msgid "Show empty block"
msgstr "Zobraziť prázdne bloky"

#: resources/views/settings.phtml:225
msgid "yes, always at standard location"
msgstr "áno, vždy na bežnom mieste"

#: resources/views/settings.phtml:225
msgid "no, but collect messages about empty blocks at the summary block"
msgstr "nie, ale zobraz správy o prázdnych blokoch v sumárnom bloku"

#: resources/views/settings.phtml:225
msgid "never"
msgstr "nikdy"

#: resources/views/settings.phtml:230
msgid ""
"Count the members of the partner chains as members of the extended family?"
msgstr "Započítať členov zreťazenia partnerov medzi členov širšej rodiny?"

#: resources/views/settings.phtml:232
msgid ""
"If you select \"no\", then the additional members in the partner chains will "
"not be counted to the total number of individuals in the extended family."
msgstr ""
"Ak zvolíte \"nie\", tak dodatoční členovia v zreťazení partnerov nebudú "
"započítaní do celkového počtu členov širšej rodiny."

#: resources/views/settings.phtml:233
msgid ""
"And these persons and families will be not selected when a user decides to "
"copy the extended family to the clippings cart."
msgstr ""
"Tieto osoby nebudú vybrané, keď sa užívateľ rozhodne kopírovať rširšiu "
"rodinu do schránky výstrižkov."

#: resources/views/settings.phtml:234
msgid ""
"But even in this case, you can copy these persons and families to the "
"clippings cart by using a special menu topic of the custom module \"enhanced "
"clippings cart\": \"add partner chains for an individual\"."
msgstr ""
"Aj v takomto prípade môžete kopírovať tieto osoby a rodiny do schránky "
"výstrižkov použitím špeciálneho bodu menu v užívateľskom module \"enhanced "
"clippings cart\": \"add partner chains for an individual\"."

#: resources/views/settings.phtml:235
msgid ""
"This is only relevant if you have chosen in the above table, that the "
"partner chains should be shown as a part of the extended family."
msgstr ""
"Toto je relevantné len v prípade, ak ste vyššie zvolili možnosť, že "
"partnerské zreťazenie má byť zobrazené ako časť širšej rodiny."

#: resources/views/settings.phtml:241
msgid "Include them"
msgstr "Zahrnúť ich"

#: resources/views/settings.phtml:249
msgid "Show parameters of extended family part?"
msgstr "Zobraziť parametre pre časti širšej rodiny?"

#: resources/views/settings.phtml:250
msgid ""
"Display of additional information for each part of the extended family, such "
"as the generation shift and the coefficient of relationship, which is a "
"measure of the degree of consanguinity."
msgstr ""
"Zobraziť dodatočné informácie pre každú časť širšej rodiny, napr. posun "
"generácie a koeficient vzťahu, ktorý je meradlom stupňa pokrvnej príbuznosti."

#: resources/views/settings.phtml:255
msgid "Show parameters"
msgstr "Zobraziť parametre"

#: resources/views/settings.phtml:263
msgid "Use the compact design?"
msgstr "Použiť kompaktný dizajn?"

#: resources/views/settings.phtml:264
msgid ""
"The compact design only shows the name and life span for each person. The "
"enriched design also shows a photo (if this is activated for this tree) as "
"well as birth and death information."
msgstr ""
"Kompaktný dizajn zobrazuje pri každej osobe len meno a roky narodenia a "
"úmrtia. Rozšírený dizajn zobrazuje fotku, ak je toto zobrazenie pre "
"príslušný strom aktivivané, ako aj údaje o narodení a úmrtí."

#: resources/views/settings.phtml:269
msgid "Use the compact design"
msgstr "Použiť kompaktný dizajn"

#: resources/views/settings.phtml:277
msgid "Which thumbnail size should be used in the enriched design?"
msgstr ""

#: resources/views/settings.phtml:278
msgid ""
"This setting affects the photo or silhouette size in the enriched design. "
"The compact design does not show thumbnails."
msgstr ""

#: resources/views/settings.phtml:283
msgid "Thumbnail size"
msgstr ""

#: resources/views/settings.phtml:291
msgid "Show name of proband as short name or as full name?"
msgstr "Zobraziť skrátené alebo plné meno probanda?"

#: resources/views/settings.phtml:292
msgid ""
"The short name is based on the probands Rufname or nickname. If these are "
"not available, the first of the given names is used, if one is given. "
"Otherwise the last name is used."
msgstr ""
"Skrátené meno je buď tzv. Rufname alebo prezývka. Ak tieto neexistujú, tak "
"sa použije prvé krstné meno. Ak ani toto neexistuje, tak sa použije "
"priezvisko."

#: resources/views/settings.phtml:297
msgid "Show short name"
msgstr "Zobraziť skrátené meno"

#: resources/views/settings.phtml:305
msgid "How should place names be shown in event boxes?"
msgstr "Ako sa majú zobraziť názvy miest v boxoch?"

#: resources/views/settings.phtml:306
msgid ""
"This setting controls whether event places are shown as full place names or "
"as abbreviated place names."
msgstr ""
"Toto nastavenie určuje, či sa zobrazí úplný názov alebo skrátený názov."

#: resources/views/settings.phtml:311
msgid "Place name format"
msgstr "Formát názvu miesta"

#: resources/views/settings.phtml:319
msgid "Show labels in special situations?"
msgstr "Zobraziť štítky pri špecifických situáciách?"

#: resources/views/settings.phtml:320
msgid ""
"Labels (or stickers) are used for example for adopted persons or foster "
"children."
msgstr ""
"Štítky sa použijú napr. pre adoptívne deti alebo deti zverené do opatery."

#: resources/views/settings.phtml:325
msgid "Show labels"
msgstr "Zobraziť štítky"

#: resources/views/settings.phtml:333
msgid "Show SOSA numbers for the proband and biological ancestors?"
msgstr ""

#: resources/views/settings.phtml:334
msgid ""
"SOSA numbers are shown as separate labels for the proband and biological "
"ancestors in the direct line."
msgstr ""

#: resources/views/settings.phtml:339
msgid "Show SOSA numbers"
msgstr ""

#: resources/views/settings.phtml:347
msgid "Show relationship to the proband as mouse-over text?"
msgstr "Zobraziť vzťah k probandovi ako text po nastavení myši?"

#: resources/views/settings.phtml:348
msgid ""
"This shows the relationship of a person to the proband when the mouse "
"pointer is over the name."
msgstr "Táto voľba zobrazí vzťah k pobandovi keď sa presunie myš nad meno."

#: resources/views/settings.phtml:356
msgid "Show relationship"
msgstr "Zobraziť vzťah"

#: resources/views/settings.phtml:364
msgid "Show a button \"Print/PDF\"?"
msgstr "Zobraziť tlačidlo \"Tlač/PDF\"?"

#: resources/views/settings.phtml:365
msgid ""
"This allows a user to open a print-optimized view and save it as a PDF file "
"from the browser print dialog."
msgstr ""
"Táto voľba umožní užívateľovi otvoriť stránku optimalizovanú na tlač a "
"uložiť ako pdf súbor z tlačového dialógu prehliadača."

#: resources/views/settings.phtml:370 resources/views/settings.phtml:389
msgid "Show button"
msgstr "Zobraziť tlačidlo"

#: resources/views/settings.phtml:378
#, fuzzy
#| msgid "Show a button \"copy to clippings cart\"?"
msgid "Show a button \"Copy to clippings cart\"?"
msgstr "Zobraziť tlačidlo \"kopírovať do schránky výstrižkov\"?"

#: resources/views/settings.phtml:379
msgid ""
"This allows a user to copy all members of the extended family to the "
"clippings cart."
msgstr ""
"Týmto sa umožňuje užívateľovi skopírovať všetkých členov širšej rodiny do "
"schránky výstrižkov."

#: resources/views/settings.phtml:401
msgid "Clippings cart action"
msgstr "Akcia schránky výstrižkov"

#: resources/views/settings.phtml:404
msgid "huhwt-cce (recommended)"
msgstr "huhwt-cce (doporučené)"

#: resources/views/settings.phtml:412
msgid "When should the extended family tab be loaded?"
msgstr "Kedy sa má načítať záložka Širšia rodina?"

#: resources/views/settings.phtml:413
msgid ""
"Choose whether the extended family tab content is calculated immediately "
"while the individual page opens or later by Ajax when the user opens the tab."
msgstr ""
"Vyberte si, či sa má obsah záložky Širšia rodina zistiť okamžite počas "
"otvárania stránky osoby, alebo pomocou ajax-u v okamihu, keď užívateľ otvorí "
"záložku."

#: resources/views/settings.phtml:418
msgid "Load later"
msgstr "Načítaj neskôr"

